//! TCP Transport for Phase 2.1 mesh receipt broadcast.
//!
//! Synchronous, length-prefixed 140-byte frames.
//! No async runtime. No ZeroMQ. Correctness-first.
//!
//! Wire format per frame:
//!   [length: u32 BE (4 bytes)][payload: 135 bytes][checksum: u8 (1 byte)]
//!   Total: 140 bytes
//!
//! The payload is the MeshReceipt wire format from mesh.rs (135 bytes).
//! The checksum is XOR of all payload bytes (fast corruption detection).
//!
//! Register: D.TRANSPORT.1.

use std::io::{self, Read, Write};
